task.summary: Just some small things on my todo list
More things on todo list. Also included some files that were somehow excluded for a long time.
Switched to a real way of doing headers in the AllShows screen. Next, Downloads.

Pumped up the Downloads screen.
Added Completed downloads. Switched to keeping things in SharedPreferences, so now it's persistent.
Fucking trying to keep ownCloud from fucking shit up.
Hopefully maybe fixed automagically moving downloads from Active to Completed on the downloads screen when they finish & it is shown, and hopefully maybe fixed clearing completed as well.

Begun moving over to Drag'n'Drop for Queue.
(Downloads should be next.)
For the love of all that is crispy and chicken, why the FUCK did my drawables get corrupted and blown up to 1.7MB
Awwwwwwww yeah, Drag-and-drop for the queue is now fully operational, though largely untested.
Overhauled the view for the Episode Description landscape. Aw yeah, it looks badass. Though that may be the rum talking.
Skinned some of the controls such as numberpicker and spinner. Hooray.
Small fix to help my OCD concerning the naming discrenpencies. And I cannot spell that word.
Queue now updates the current track as it is playing.
Bulked up support for /* commands in the IRC. Especially op stuff and modes.
